1,window linux 子系统和 liunx 系统都要装上 ssh
2, window 防火墙要关闭
3，设置网络，一根网线直连两台电脑，
windows 端：ip:192.168.1.1 
    	    netmask:255.255.255.0
            gateway:192.168.1.1(与ip相同，此为网关)
	    dns:不设
linux 端: static ip: 192.168.1.102
                 netmast: same as windows
                 gateway: same as window
                 dns: same as gateway

